flowchart TD
    A[User sends request<br/>with Plan Mode active] --> B[Claude explores the codebase<br/>Read, Grep, Glob]
    B --> C{Need clarifications?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Claude asks questions<br/>Question Tool]
    D --> E[User responds]
    E --> B
    C -->|No| F[Claude formulates the plan<br/>with approach and steps]
    F --> G{User approves?}
    G -->|Change requested| H[Claude revises the plan]
    H --> G
    G -->|Rejects| I[Claude rethinks<br/>the approach]
    I --> B
    G -->|Approves| J[Plan execution<br/>writing tools reactivated]
    J --> K[Implementation<br/>with the plan as guide]
